<br><br><lang=en><i>English translation</i><br>Zapatista House-Barracks of <b>General Leobardo Galván González</b><br>The only person from Morelos who participated from the beginning in the work of the "Sovereign Revolutionary Convention" in Aguascalientes (1914-1916).</b><br>
<br>
